===Manga===
The manga was launched in the December issue of [[Shogakukan]]'s ''Monthly Hero's'' magazine on October 31, 2015.<ref name="Infini-T"/> It was written by Ukyō Kodachi and illustrated by [[Tatsuma Ejiri]]. [[Udon Entertainment]] announced during their [[Anime Expo]] 2017 panel that they have licensed the manga.<ref>{{cite web|title=Udon Licenses Infini-T Force Manga With Limited Pre-Launch at Anime Expo|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-06-21/udon-licenses-infini-t-force-manga-with-limited-pre-launch-at-anime-expo/.117790|website=Anime News Network|accessdate=December 6, 2017|date=June 21, 2017}}</ref>

